    <!-- Quick Wins Section -->
    <div class="content-section">
        <h2 id="quick-wins">⚡ Quick Wins - If AI Chat Phases Complete Early</h2>
        
        <p><strong>From Priority Matrix: High Importance, Low-to-Medium Effort</strong></p>
        <p>If AI Chat verification (Phases 1-4) completes by 2 PM, consider these quick wins that can be marked complete:</p>

        <h3>Quick Win 1: A.3 Credentials Audit - Planning Phase (~2 hours)</h3>
        <div style="background: #d4edda; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 15px 0; border-left: 4px solid #28a745;">
            <p><strong>Status:</strong> 🔴 CRITICAL importance, 🟡 MEDIUM effort (1 week to execute, 2 hours to plan)</p>
            <p><strong>What:</strong> Review where all API credentials/secrets are stored (Proxmox, Cloudflare, Ollama). Audit security: Are they in version control? Hardcoded? Using secure vaults?</p>
            <p><strong>Quick Planning Task (2 hours max):</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Search codebase for hardcoded API keys: `grep -r "api_key\|password\|secret" lib/ config/`</li>
                <li>List all files: `.env.development`, `.env.staging`, `db_config.json`, `cloudflare_config.json`, credential files</li>
                <li>Create document: Where each credential is stored, are they in .gitignore?</li>
                <li>Add to Master Plan: This blocks B.1/B.2 (Docker Secrets, Auth fixes)</li>
            </ul>
            <p><strong>Achievable Today?</strong> ✅ YES - planning/audit phase. Actual fix is Phase 2.</p>
        </div>

        <h3>Quick Win 2: B.3 Theme Handling - Audit Phase (~1.5 hours)</h3>
        <div style="background: #d4edda; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 15px 0; border-left: 4px solid #28a745;">
            <p><strong>Status:</strong> 🟠 HIGH importance, 🟡 MEDIUM effort</p>
            <p><strong>What:</strong> Check if theme system has known issues. Are theme CSS variables working? Do per-site themes apply correctly?</p>
            <p><strong>Quick Audit Task (1.5 hours max):</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Test: Navigate to 3 different sites and verify theme CSS loads correctly</li>
                <li>Check: `root/static/css/themes/` directory - what themes exist?</li>
                <li>Verify: `theme_definitions.json` has mappings for all sites</li>
                <li>Test: Are CSS variables working? (--primary-color, --text-color, etc.)</li>
                <li>Document findings: What works, what needs fixing?</li>
            </ul>
            <p><strong>Achievable Today?</strong> ✅ YES - audit phase. Can move to fix phase if issues found.</p>
            <p><strong>📋 Audit Report:</strong> <a href="/Documentation/B3ThemeHandlingAuditReport" target="_blank" class="doc-link">B3ThemeHandlingAuditReport</a> - Comprehensive findings and refactoring recommendations</p>
        </div>

        <h3>Quick Win 3: Master Plan Improvements (Ongoing - Add as found)</h3>
        <div style="background: #e3f2fd; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 15px 0; border-left: 4px solid #1976d2;">
            <p><strong>Document Missing Components Found During AI Chat Testing:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Missing Result classes for other tables?</li>
                <li>Missing controllers or routes that should exist?</li>
                <li>Documentation gaps discovered?</li>
                <li>Schema mismatches between code and database?</li>
            </ul>
            <p><strong>Action:</strong> When found, add to Master Plan in a new section: "Improvements & Missing Components Identified During E.1 Implementation"</p>
        </div>
    </div>

